          "model": "grok-1.5"
        },
        {
          "id": "s108",
          "content": "晉唐叔虞，武王子。初封。",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
          "model": "grok-1.5"
        },
        {
          "id": "s109",
          "content": "秦惡來，助紂。父飛廉，有力。",
