          "model": "grok-1.5"
        },
        {
          "id": "s110",
          "content": "楚熊繹。繹父鬻熊，事文王。初封。",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
          "model": "grok-1.5"
        },
        {
          "id": "s111",
          "content": "宋微子啟，紂庶兄。初封。",
